Module hu.unipannon.virt.plot
Package hu.unipannon.virt.plot.frame

Class Frame

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent
        • javafx.scene.Group
          • hu.unipannon.virt.plot.frame.Container
            • hu.unipannon.virt.plot.frame.Frame
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
    public class Frame
extends Container
    Highest level Container class of the graphical system. The Frame class contains all components of the graphical Plot. Components can be turned on with the show... and off with the hide... methods.
    Author:
    Tóth Bálint
    See Also:
    PlotSpace, HorizontalAxis, VerticalAxis, Container
